# Private operator notes — NOT for public GitBook.
# Reasons:
#   client01.md       contains demo passwords (admin1234 / demo1234)
#   ops_metrics.md    contains SSH key paths + EC2 IPs + RDS internal hostname
#   SECRETS.md        filename alone is a red flag; superseded by docs/security/secret-management.md
#   docs/quickstart.md  superseded by docs/introduction/quickstart.md
#   docs/runbooks/    superseded by docs/operations/runbooks/
docs/client01.md
docs/ops_metrics.md
docs/SECRETS.md
docs/quickstart.md
docs/runbooks/

